'''Spaceship Hangout''' is a [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|world]] created by SpaceJackalTim published in May of 2021.

The setting is a Spaceship where you are the Captain of the vessel where you can explore diffrent planets and stars to change the environment around the ship, The external view is visable from select locations onboard with the execption of the Theater and Engineering having no external viewing.

Each Planet (and other locations) has its own Lore and information about its history and its current state when you vist them, Discovery of all planets and other locations are randomly generated when an [[Special:MyLanguage/Instances|Instance]] is created.
==Airlock Entryway==
Once you are onboard your vessel you will appear in the Docking/Airlock where you are greeted by modifications made to the ship (world updates) and credits for assets used inside the [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|World]].

Apon going to the Left from the airlock exit the crew section including dorms and the soical area which has a bar and spin the bottle with viewing screens for the [[Special:MyLanguage/Video players|video player]]

It makes a great vibrant environment for socializing and drinking at the bar.

Mirrors in this world don't seem to turn themselfs off, It's recommend you disable the mirrors before leaving the rooms.

All door buttons are accessable vai Pushing with the Index finger or simply clicking the button.

