==Crew Area==
In the crew area there are number of locations

Inside the bar/entertainment area:

* Spin the bottle
*Open face bar with working Coffee Maker set (interactable)
*Full playing card deck, Standard faces. (reset button on wall (Notlocal))
*Seats
*Video players
*Mirrors
*Collider toggles & Chair toggles
