==Captains Quarter==
At the end of the Hallway from the left of the airlock exit is the Captains quarter, Filled with the real luxury parts of the Ship, The captain is determined by the name at the top of the doorway of the entrance to the quarter.

All the selected space luxarys inside are as listed:

*Giantd L Sofa for relaxing
*Queen sized bed with collider/Doorlock/Sleep mode and Mirror toggles on the walls
* Ceiling Air conditioning for quiet background noise
*Full operating Shower with Mirror
*
*A full view of the outside of the ship through 3 seperate bulkheads with mirror toggle in the center.
<gallery widths="300" heights="164" mode="nolines">
File:SSHO CaptainsQuarterKB7.png|The captain quarters with the bed and Kepler-7B In view outside the windows.
</gallery>

==Theater Area==
Apon Exiting the Airlock and heading to your right the first door on your left will let you enter the theater Area.

The theater area has optional [[Real time probes|Real time probles]] which reflects the video display across the room dependent on whats on Screen, There are optional seats for desktop users and VR users can disable them at entry as they are enabled by default.<gallery widths="300" heights="180">
File:SSHO VP-RT-Off.webp|Real time probes disabled.
File:SSHO VP-RT-On.webp|Real time probes enabled.
</gallery>

